GBM-Subtype: Glioblastoma subtype. Values obtained from UCSC Cancer Genomics Browser
tumor_tissue_site: The tissue site of the tumour
icluster: iCluster Plus: Pattern discovery and cancer gene identification in integrated cancer genomic data.
CofC: Integrated subtype classification for all of the tumor samples in the Pan-Cancer collection based on five data platforms
RPPA-cluster: Expression data for 131 proteins and 3467 Pancancer tumor samples, measured by RPPA (reverse phase protein array) technology
mutation_data: Mutation data in matrix for the sample
cna_data: CNA data in matrix for the sample
rnaseq_data: RNA-seq data in matrix for the sample
